title: 2020 Week 7 Preview
itunes:title: 2020 Week 7 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler preview every game of the upcoming weekend, but first have some very important Ravens news to report on. (2:30) Dan gets the first pick and chooses the two undefeated teams (4:30) and Gregg is excited for Jimmy G back to New England (11:44). Marc surprises the guys with a lock (sarcasm!) and chooses the Seahawks, again (26:07). Dan is excited for the Bills/Jets game (1:09:05) and there is a surprising lock off (1:16:00).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
